descr: "Related artifacts such as additional documentation, justification, or bibliographic references."

fields.name: type
fields.descr: "The type of relationship to the related artifact."

fields.name: display
fields.descr: "A brief description of the document or knowledge resource being referenced, suitable for display to a consumer."

fields.name: citation
fields.descr: "A bibliographic citation for the related artifact. This text SHOULD be formatted according to an accepted citation format."

fields.name: url
fields.descr: "A url for the artifact that can be followed to access the actual content."

fields.name: document
fields.descr: "The document being referenced, represented as an attachment. This is exclusive with the resource element."

fields.name: id
fields.descr:
"unique id for the element within a resource (for internal references). This may be any string value that does not contain spaces."
